title: 1MDB Sale for Power Assets Draws Tepid Response
text:
A crucial asset sale by an embattled Malaysian government investment fund met with tepid response from bidders on Friday, with the only known bid being a “conditional” offer from another state-owned power producer.
Bids for power plants owned by 1Malaysia Development Bhd., or 1MDB, were due Friday, and other potential buyers who had expressed interest didn’t appear to make offers for the plants.
